import React from 'react'

const Search = props => {
  <Button
    variant="contained"
    color="primary"
    className='add-beer'
    onClick={this.toggleBeerInput}>
    Click here to search for a beer!
  </Button>
  {
    this.props.isSearching &&
    <Input placeholder="Search Cooler" onChange={this.fuzzySearch}> </Input>
  }
}
